data.title: List of NOTAMS for Your Area
data.text:
NOTAM list for anonymous user for

ALL the current UK NOTAMS are listed here

To get a list for your location only, log on, or create an account, and specify your location.

You may click on each NOTAM reference to see that NOTAM on your local map. Click on the 'Q' code reference to see an explanation of the codes and text. If you have donated to the web site, you can also remove any NOTAM from the maps, if they are not of interest. (You can reverse this whenever you like). If you view the printer-friendly version of this list, it will not show the removed NOTAMs
